+
+config ROCKCHIP_MPP_RKVDEC2
+	bool "RKVDEC2 (VDPU381) H.264/H.265/VP9 decoder"
+	default y
+	help
+	  Hardware video decoder VDPU381 (rkvdec2) found on RK3588: two decoder
+	  cores plus a CCU. H.264, H.265 and VP9 decode. Builds the
+	  mpp_rkvdec2 + mpp_rkvdec2_link objects into rk_vcodec.ko.
+
+config ROCKCHIP_MPP_RKVDEC2_DEVFREQ
+	bool "RKVDEC2 devfreq/OPP/system-monitor (tier-2)"
+	depends on ROCKCHIP_MPP_RKVDEC2 && PM_DEVFREQ
+	default n
+	help
+	  Enable the devfreq/OPP/system-monitor DVFS island for rkvdec2. Off by
+	  default; the decoder runs at fixed assigned-clock-rates without it.
